title: how we make money on social media!
itunes:title: how we make money on social media!
description:
Brooke and Danielle are breaking down their various streams of income!  As full time social media content creators, the gals are often asked how they make money/get paid. Brooke and Danielle share all of their social media streams of income, explain a little more about their “teams”, and share helpful tips for aspiring influencers to earn some extra $!
